4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT PROHIBITING THE FLUORIDATION OF PUBLIC WATER
5 SUPPLY SYSTEMS; AND AMENDING SECTIONS 75-6-112 AND 76-4-104, MCA.”
6
7 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF MONTANA:
